title: NPCC sweeps Region IX rival Southeast
text:
Previous Next NPCC sweeps Region IX rival Southeast 
Josie Palmer and Jessica Lovitt, of the North Platte Knights volleyball team, try to block a shot against Southeast on Wednesday at McDonald-Belton Gymnasium. (Andrew Bottrell / The North Platte Telegraph) Posted: Wednesday, October 7, 2015 8:35 pm 
The North Platte Knights volleyball team exacted some revenge on Region IX foe Southeast on Wednesday, sweeping the Storm 25-15, 25-22, 25-17 at McDonald-Belton Gymnasium. 
The Storm swept the Knights on Sept. 24 in Beatrice.     Subscription required
